snippet.title: Jeff Su
snippet.description:
üåü This is the channel I wish I could have subscribed when I first entered the workforce

I'm Jeff, a full time Product Marketer. In my spare time I like to tinker with tools and create systems that help me get things done faster - or as one of my friends puts it: "Get better at being lazy" üòè

I make videos on practical career and productivity tips without all the "fluff"

So if you're a college student, working professional, or super ambitious high schooler, make sure to subscribe to my channel üí°
